parameters:
Hikomaru: "To think I'd come all this way just to buy bloomers...
You're a teacher from Shoutou Academy, right? Why is the pickup
location at Shousei Academy?"
Dokushima: "Sorry... but it can't be helped."

Dokushima: "I was kicked out of that academy. Just loitering around
the place gets me cold stares from everyone."

Hikomaru: "You brought it upon yourself... Stealing bloomers might go
unnoticed, but if you mess with the girls, of course this would
happen."
Dokushima: "I had been managing it well until now..."
Dokushima: "But damn it, that Morisaki... I'll never forgive her!!"

Dokushima: "Yeah, just thinking about it pisses me off. I was looking
out for her, and she repaid my kindness with betrayal..."

Hikomaru: "...Anyway, let's get on with the transaction. We can't stay
long even if Shousei Academy is closed."

Dokushima: "Isn't this your alma mater? I chose this place because
it's safe."

Dokushima: "Well, it was bad of me to suddenly change the meeting
place. I stole a bunch before I got dismissed, so I'll sell them to
you cheap today."

Dokushima: "I've brought some top-notch items with the sweet smell of
sweat and stains. Take a look!"
Yui: (So the thefts at the academy were Dokushima's doing...)
Yui: "Hey, you two! I heard everything!"
Yui: "I want you to return the bloomers you stole from the girls!"

Dokushima: "How do you know her? She's the very person who got me
fired, the Morisaki we were just talking about!"
Dokushima: "Looks like you've got your own issues with Morisaki..."
Hikomaru: "Please do something, teacher! I can't handle her..."
Dokushima: "Hey, let's get out of here!"
